A desperate appeal has been made to the public to assist in the search of Luschka and Daniel Taljaard after they went missing from their home in Hendrina at about 09:00 this morning. Coetzee Taljaard, Luschka’s husband, confirmed this evening that their disappearances have been reported at the SAPS and the VW Polo they were travelling in was found abandoned at Kwazamokuhle’s entrance. Should anyone have information that could assist in the search thay can contact Investigator Anthony Boucher from SA Investigations and Security at 071 290 7423, Coetzee Taljaard at 079 713 4637 or Esther Zeeman at 065 311 5691.